{"tid":2343701,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"想講下「廢青」呢樣野","createTime":"2020-12-28T06:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T11:50:28.000Z","uid":344464,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b98ecd1d97848b43f60618266e344c0cd960806d","tid":2343701,"uid":344464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T06:37:41.000Z","msg":"屌你老母其實所謂廢青真係好撚慘， 真係諗唔明啲父母，明明係為咗私利生個仔出嚟，跟住又要人受苦唔知幾多10年，做啲人哋唔想做嘅嘢，唔做就係廢青，公平咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你唔資助個仔買啲貴到戇鳩嘅樓都算，仲要人畀家用？唔畀就係不孝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />慘到...<br />\n<br />\n如果我生仔，一定會諗埋點幫佢未來生活，而唔係佢點幫我未來生活囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以你班友可唔可以咪再鬧追求自由嘅廢青？"},{"pid":"bcdfdc034d5e17e05a680128ab69d897ffb7984e","tid":2343701,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T06:39:00.000Z","msg":"hi 廢青"},{"pid":"4f2eae93ad1e8bcb7bc7c0f34af4c176ae7e2bf8","tid":2343701,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T06:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11bd16bb7986eebcc134b1076f57827d1fcaa97b","tid":2343701,"uid":240481,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T06:40:24.000Z","msg":"香港地做廢青嘅門檻好低<br />\n只要你搵唔到錢 就係廢青<br />\n所以做香港人係好慘"},{"pid":"ba649ff8f1ec36454b83023c23684344cb898c8b","tid":2343701,"uid":344464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T06:41:02.000Z","msg":"例子：<br />\n<br />\n有個廢青係屋企都幾麻煩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2218347\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2218347</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n啲人就最撚鍾意怪啲兄弟姊妹廢，而唔係怪父母"},{"pid":"5028910086925d87da16fb0e566c242a176f29d0","tid":2343701,"uid":220009,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"